import {useState} from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Button,
  CheckboxIcon,
  Flex,
  Image,
  Input,
  Select,

import axios from 'axios';
import {encode ,decode} from 'iconv-lite';

  setState({

          <Box py="50px" px="50px" bg="#f2f2f2" flex="1" id="footer">

                    borderColor={"#000"}

                    w="100%"
                    name="detailAddress"
                    onChange={changeState}
                    borderWidth="1px"
                    borderColor={"#000"}

              </Flex>
              <Flex gap="10px">
                <Show breakpoint="(min-width: 1000px)">
                  <Text m="0px" minW="100px">

                  name="QA"
                  onChange={changeState}
                  resize={"none"}

                  borderColor={"#000"}

                    height: "30px",
                    borderColor: "#000",

                    borderRadius: "4px",
                    backgroundColor: "#fff",

                  h="30px"
                  w="100%"

              <Flex gap="10px">
                <Show breakpoint="(min-width: 1000px)">

                    w="100%"

                    borderColor={"#000"}

                    value={state.addres}
                    onChange={changeState}

                    h="30px"
                    w="100%"
                    borderWidth="1px"
                    borderColor={"#000"}
                    name="detailAddres"
                    value={state.detailAddres}

              <Flex gap="10px">
                <Show breakpoint="(min-width: 1000px)">
                  <Text m="0px" minW="100px">

                  w="100%"
                  resize={"none"}
                  borderWidth="1px"
                  borderColor={"#000"}
                  name="QA"
                  value={state.QA}
                  onChange={changeState}
                />
              </Flex>
              <CheckboxIcon />
              <Flex gap="10px">
                <Show breakpoint="(min-width: 1000px)">
                  <Text m="0px" minW="100px"></Text>
                </Show>
                <Button
                  w="100%"
                  bg="#2B2B2B"
                  h="45px"
                  color="#fff"
                  fontWeight={"bold"}
                  fontSize="18px"
                  onClick={sendSms}
                >
                  견적 문의하기
                </Button>
              </Flex>
            </Flex>
          </Box>
        </Flex>
      </Show>
    </>

};

export default Body9;
